<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_28" id="13v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_28_r4l13"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Balthaſar von Maſpach <expan>Tumh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l14">cʒu <expan>wirʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> vnd <expan>Probſt<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒu Onlſpach </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_28_r4l15">Erſamer vnd lıeber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough">vns hat furgelegt Jacob Topler </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l16">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Burger </del> / Als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erſamkeit vormals <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l17">von Jacob Toplers <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>B<ex>urgers</ex></expan> / vnd der <expan>leh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvegen / die Er von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l18">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan></del> ew hat / vnd die gern <expan>empfah<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wolt . / Alſo hat vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l19">derſelb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> fürgelegt / vvie daʒ 
<add><ab facs="#facs_28_line_1576489786819_6870">Jr </ab></add> Jm noch niht <expan>gelih<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l20">ſunder Jm das <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒogen</expan> vnd Jm darümb <expan>cʒuantvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l22">
<add><ab facs="#facs_28_r4l21">vnd maint daʒ Jr Jm niht ſchuldıg ſeit <expan>ʒuleih<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> vnd maint / daʒ Jr Jm niht ſchuldig ſeit <expan>cʒuleih<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd daʒ Jr </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l24">
<add><ab facs="#facs_28_r3l1">vnd </ab></add> Im 
<add><ab facs="#facs_28_r4l23">darümb </ab></add> <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> tag 
<del rend="strikethrough"> vor ſant Michels tag </del> für die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> b </del> gen <expan>vvırcʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l25">oder gen Onlſpach <expan>beſcheide<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd die do erkennen laſſen wöll
<del rend="strikethrough">et </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l28">ob Jr Jm <expan>leih<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſöll
<del rend="strikethrough">et </del> oder niht / vnd 
<add><ab facs="#facs_28_r4l26">vvolt Jn des </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> Jn darumb ein </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_28_line_1576489801860_6886">ewr </ab></add> <expan>verſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l31"> <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wiſſen laſſen vor ſant Michels tag 
<add><ab facs="#facs_28_line_1576489812820_6898"><expan>nehſv<ex>er</ex>gangen</expan> </ab></add> / ob Jr das alſo cʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_line_1576489842387_6925"> <expan>vvircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> oder cʒu Onlſpach 
<add><ab facs="#facs_28_line_1576489844881_6930">tun </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>erkenne<ex>n</ex></expan> laſſen </del> vvölt / des 
<del rend="strikethrough"> der v </del> Er biſʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l38">her gevvartet hab 
<add><ab facs="#facs_28_line_1576489846634_6935">das Jm doch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒogen</expan> </ab></add> / vnd Jm 
<del rend="strikethrough"> doch </del> khein <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> noch von ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l39"><expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_28_line_1576489864180_6956">ſey </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſey vnd Jm <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒogen</expan> ſeẏ </del> / des er vaſt <expan>ſchade<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_line_1576489880282_6970">hab vnd neme / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr noch dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> durch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l42"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>gnedıklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>leih<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / oder Jm aber in 
<del rend="strikethrough"><gap reason="illegible"/></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_28_line_1576489882241_6975">den nehſten </ab></add> xiiij tagen 
<del rend="strikethrough">noch </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l43"> <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> tag 
<del rend="strikethrough">beſcheiden </del> für die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough">b</del> gen <expan>wircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> oder gen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l44">Onlſpach <expan>beſcheide<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd do <expan>erkenne<ex>n</ex></expan> laſſen / vvöllet / ob Jr Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l45"><expan>leih<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſüllet oder niht / Das woͤllen etc <expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l47">Anno ix<hi rend="sup">no</hi>$ $</ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_28" id="13v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Balthasar von Maspach,
                            <expan>tumh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czu <expan>Wirzb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
                        und <expan>probst<ex>en</ex></expan> czu Onlspach </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Ersamer und lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> ersamkeit vormals
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Jacob Toplers,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>, und der <expan>leh<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wegen, die er von ew hat und die gern <expan>empfah<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wolt.
                        Also hat uns derselb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> fürgelegt, wie daz <add>ir</add> im noch
                        niht <expan>gelih<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, sunder im das
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>czogen</expan> und im darümb
                                <expan>czuantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt <add>und maint, daz ir im niht schuldig
                            seit <expan>zuleih<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add>
<add>und</add> im <add>darümb</add>
<expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> tag für die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gen
                                <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> oder gen Onlspach
                                <expan>bescheide<ex>n</ex></expan> und die do erkennen lassen wöll,
                        ob ir im <expan>leih<ex>e</ex>n</expan> söll oder niht; und <add>wolt in
                            des</add>
<add>ewr</add>
<expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wissen lassen vor <app><note><q type="date">sant Michels tag
                                <add><expan>nehsv<ex>er</ex>gangen</expan></add></q>29.09.1409</note></app>, ob ir das also
                        czu <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> oder czu Onlspach <add>tun</add> wölt,
                        des er biszher gewartet hab, <add>das im doch
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>czogen</expan></add> und im khein
                                <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> noch von ew
                            <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>sey</add>, des er vast <expan>schade<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hab und neme.
                            <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir noch dem
                                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>leih<ex>e</ex>n</expan> oder im aber in <add>den nehsten</add> xiiii
                        tagen <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> tag für die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        gen <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> oder gen Onlspach
                                <expan>bescheide<ex>n</ex></expan> und do
                            <expan>erkenne<ex>n</ex></expan> lassen wöllet, ob ir im
                                <expan>leih<ex>e</ex>n</expan> süllet oder niht. Das woͤllen etc.
                                <expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan> anno ix<hi rend="sup">no</hi>.</ab>
</div>
